Ya sudah, ayo berangkat.

00:22:20.030 --> 00:22:22.400
So don't you worry♪

00:22:22.400 --> 00:22:26.910
Tanpa bisa kamu sadari♪

00:22:26.910 --> 00:22:31.540
Semoga dirimu terlindungi♪

